data.description: A Lovely Maintained Home With Lots Of Updates featuring 5 bedrooms and 2 bath, Updated Kitchen with Stainless steel appliances, Updated Bathrooms, Siding 2011, Roof 2011, Garage for storage, shed at the back, Stone Fireplace. Updated Windows. Quiet Mid-Block Location. Formal Dining Room. Dormered And Expanded Upstairs. Laundry Room. Wood Floors Throughout. A Must See!! Will Not Last!! This house is close to shopping mall and public transportation.
